QuestData.Title: Daughter of the Sea
QuestData.Description:
They're not letting us any closer to the keep. We'll have to walk from here.
Returning to Boralus has stirred feelings I thought I'd left behind. Memories smoothed away by the years like stones in the tide.
It all feels raw again.
I do not know how this will end--only that we must try.
QuestData.LogDescription: Accompany Jaina Proudmoore to an audience with Katherine Proudmoore.
QuestData.RewardText: Hope you had a nice nap. You're gonna need your strength.
